NNQT_istance: Which continents contain bodyofwaters whith a mean areaofcatchments greater than 4000?
correct_NNQT_istance: Which continents contain bodyofwaters with a mean areaofcatchments greater than 4000?
query:
SELECT ?area WHERE { 
	?area rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Continent>. 
	?uri rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BodyOfWater>. 
	?uri  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/areaOfCatchment> ?measure.   
	?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> ?area .  }GROUP BY ?area HAVING( AVG(?measure)>4000)
